<div class="container ">
  <h1 class="text-center">About Me</h1>
  <div class="row">
    <%= image_tag 'steve.jpg', class: 'col-xs-3 col-xs-offset-1' %>
    <p class="col-xs-6">
      Stephen A. Akuffo works as a Pre-sales Solution Specialist at Dell Technologies. He has consulted with many small and medium size businesses to help them map IT infrastructure strategies and technology acquisition decisions.

      Stephen is certified on multiple Dell and VMware Technologies. He carries a VMware Certified Professional certification and is a vExpert 2016

